{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525660/extras/FightHeader.png?t=1728871234\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525660/extras/DWCombatGif.gif?t=1728871234\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Launch foes into the air and juggle them with relentless attacks.<br></li><li> Backstab and Parry enemies then land a devastating charged attack.<br></li><li> Build up your combo meter for buffs to change the tide of battle.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525660/extras/LevelHeader.png?t=1728871234\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525660/extras/LevelingAxesSmaller.jpg?t=1728871234\" /><br></li><li> Slay foes and gather devil shards to level up.<br></li><li> Build into a fighting style of your choice.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525660/extras/ExploreHeader.png?t=1728871234\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525660/extras/ExplorePictureSmall.png?t=1728871234\" /><br></li><li> Search every corner of Grimthorn for upgrades and weapons.<br></li><li> Find Sub-Weapons, Items and Gear to augment your abilities and fighting style to give you a edge in battle.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525660/extras/SurviveHeader.png?t=1728871234\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2525660/extras/SurvivePictureAlt.png?t=1728871234\" /><br></li><li> Fight multiple bosses with unique movesets.<br></li><li> Dodge overwhelmingly powerful attacks and avoid stunning barrages.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as